==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bùxiào yŏu sān, wú hòu wéi dà

===Etymology===
A quote from ''[[w:Mencius|Mencius]]'' ([[孟子]])
===Proverb===
'''[[不孝]][[有]][[三]]，[[無]][[後]][[為]][[大]]'''
# There are three ways to be unfilial, the worst is to not produce off-spring.

===Alternate forms===
[[不孝有三，无后为大]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
